title: 149: The ALDI Haul Episode (July '21 Edition)
itunes:title: The ALDI Haul Episode (July '21 Edition)
description: In this week’s episode, Lisa, Jamie, and Mikey are taste-testing some really great finds like a tasty meatless chicken patty, cauliflower pizza, keto hamburger buns, fruit on the bottom non-fat Greek yogurt, salsa, and SO MUCH MORE! Plus, you’ll have to tune in for the find of the week, which received a perfect 10 on Lisa’s scale! So stop everything, push play, and then when you’re done, head on over to our Foodcast page for a list of all the finds mentioned in the episode!
itunes:summary: We did it again… We went back to ALDI and discovered SO MANY amazing finds!
itunes:author: Lisa Lillien
